tool_input.script:
export const meta = {
  name: 'qa-semantic-search',
  description: 'Execute semantic search for QA workflow',
  phases: [
    { title: 'Semantic Search', detail: 'Search knowledge files for relevant sections' }
  ]
}

phase('Semantic Search')
const result = await agent(
  `Execute the semantic search workflow defined in workflows/semantic-search.md.

Working directory: /home/tie303177/work/nabledge/work2/.claude/skills/nabledge-6

The query is:
"APサーバを複数台にスケールアウトするとき、セッション変数の保存先はどれを選ぶべき？各ストアの特徴を知りたい（処理方式: ウェブアプリケーション）（目的: 仕組み・動作を理解したい）"

Read the file workflows/semantic-search.md and follow it exactly.

For each page you consider, record:
- why it was selected or skipped

For each section you consider, record:
- why it was selected (high/partial) or skipped

Return a JSON object with:
{
  "selected_sections": [
    {"file": "<full path to knowledge file>", "section_id": "<sN>", "relevance": "<high|partial>", "reason": "<why selected>"}
  ],
  "selected_pages": [
    {"path": "<page path relative to knowledge/>", "reason": "<why selected>"}
  ],
  "excluded_pages": [
    {"path": "<page path relative to knowledge/>", "reason": "<why skipped>"}
  ],
  "excluded_sections": [
    {"file": "<full path>", "section_id": "<sN>", "reason": "<why skipped>"}
  ]
}`,
  { schema: {
    type: 'object',
    properties: {
      selected_sections: {
        type: 'array',
        items: {
          type: 'object',
          properties: {
            file: { type: 'string' },
            section_id: { type: 'string' },
            relevance: { type: 'string', enum: ['high', 'partial'] },
            reason: { type: 'string' }
          },
          required: ['file', 'section_id', 'relevance', 'reason']
        }
      },
      selected_pages: {
        type: 'array',
        items: {
          type: 'object',
          properties: {
            path: { type: 'string' },
            reason: { type: 'string' }
          },
          required: ['path', 'reason']
        }
      },
      excluded_pages: {
        type: 'array',
        items: {
          type: 'object',
          properties: {
            path: { type: 'string' },
            reason: { type: 'string' }
          },
          required: ['path', 'reason']
        }
      },
      excluded_sections: {
        type: 'array',
        items: {
          type: 'object',
          properties: {
            file: { type: 'string' },
            section_id: { type: 'string' },
            reason: { type: 'string' }
          },
          required: ['file', 'section_id', 'reason']
        }
      }
    },
    required: ['selected_sections', 'selected_pages', 'excluded_pages', 'excluded_sections']
  }}
)

return result
